level.text: A motion to file documents under seal may be filed and served electronically. Redacted copies of documents filed under seal may be filed and served electronically; however, documents filed under seal containing privileged information shall be filed in paper form.

level.heading: SOURCE
level.text: Final Rulemaking published at 49 DCR 2078 (March 8, 2002); as amended by Emergency and Proposed Rulemaking published at 52 DCR 4782 (May 20, 2005) [EXPIRED].
